At times very funny anecdotes are shared amongst the audience,always interesting and informative stories. Excellent backing band (selected by Ricky Scaggs)(and why wouldn't they be brilliant as most are constantly used in Scaggs band anyway)
I will be collecting more Country Family Reunion dvd's.
